<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB01428</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT INSTITUTING THE FREE NUTRI-MEALS PROGRAM IN PUBLIC ELEMENTARY AND SECONDARY SCHOOLS, PROVIDING MECHANISMS FOR ITS IMPLEMENTATION, APPROPRIATING FUNDS THEREFOR, AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SHORT TITLE : Free Nutri-meals Program Of 2016</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Directs the government to take a concerted efforts to institutionalize a Free Nutri-Meals Program for children in all public elementary and secondary schools to tackle the problem of hunger and malnutrition and to realize marked improvement in the attendance, nutrition, health and academic performances of the Filipino school children.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>TUPAS, RAUL &quot;BOBOY&quot; C.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2016-07-12</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>NATURE : Welfare</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Ong (H.) (004 2016-08-01)</td><td>2. Catamco (017 2016-08-31)</td><tr><td>3. Mangaoang (025 2016-09-21)</td><td>4. Gorriceta (025 2016-09-21)</td><tr><td>5. Palma (025 2016-09-21)</td><td>6. Yu (025 2016-09-21)</td><tr><td>7. Defensor (025 2016-09-21)</td><td>8. Madrona (025 2016-09-21)</td><tr><td>9. Espino (025 2016-09-21)</td><td>10. Eusebio (025 2016-09-21)</td><tr><td>11. Vargas (029 2016-09-29)</td><td>12. Bataoil (029 2016-09-29)</td><tr><td>13. Dalipe (051 2016-12-05)</td><td>14. Nava (055 2016-12-13)</td><tr><td>15. Gasataya (055 2016-12-13)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>COMMITEE HEARINGS/ACTIONS:</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp1. Referred to Stakeholders on 2016-09-14</b><tr><td colspan=3>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp-DepED</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&